        "body": "Three kinetic album identities for ND Music, a label for digital artists. Each record carries its own concept and atmosphere within one shared visual language — radial kinetic type in a black, white and orange palette. Built as a modular motion system in Cavalry, every identity ships across formats: Spotify-style vertical video, square video and a static cover."
