        "label": "",
        "heading": "Three Records, One System",
        "body": "One shared visual direction flexed into three distinct records: Self Control (radial dashes collapsing inward), Why Don't You Stay (restless repeating wave-type) and Maze of Memories (a spinning black-orange pinwheel)."
