        "label": "",
        "heading": "Built to Move",
        "body": "In Cavalry the identity is a modular motion system: one set of rules drives every output. The same language scales from a Spotify story to a square loop to an event poster (Live in Zurich, Feb 2026) — animated, adaptable and always on-brand."
